{"tid":1691614,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online] 打完鋪機覺得需要檢討下","createTime":"2019-11-03T17:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T14:36:10.000Z","uid":185767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"422bb8eb6b9815bb033ccefc4de16d192ddba6b5","tid":1691614,"uid":185767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"琴日打左幾舖機。<br />\n第一舖，係銅記靠木橋入左圍圓，入到去發現所有岀入口比敵方既怪封住。之後敵方既怪更加係無被衝擊下會捉我方兵仔。跟住一路被逼由天後跑至銅記。再要逃離香島。當中我方已犧牲多兵！<br />\n我認為呢舖機真係好有問題，我認為有需要檢討及改善我方戰術！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我強調不分化！不割席！<br />\n檢討係為左進步，減小犧牲！</span>"},{"pid":"3f2ced676334deb92e9d61ceb986147d8b93bc14","tid":1691614,"uid":185767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:41:43.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"0afe1cb5101a5f8ee1e2205b1043e39d271db36c","tid":1691614,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:11:38.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b42930009a211946c1fef55228956de507489549","tid":1691614,"uid":185767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"f6e977fef9a5f01d21a2db10b6052607d2d2bc2a","tid":1691614,"uid":185767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"2/10"}]}